{% extends 'src/partials/layout.njk'%}
{% block content %}
<header class="w-full xl:h-[907px] h-[410px] bg-cover bg-center bg-red-600" style="background-image: url('/pussiveskiasi.jpg');">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center xl:flex-row xl:justify-items-center xl:pt-[289px] pt-[130px]">
    <h1 class="font-beardbone xl:text-left text-center select-none xl:text-[300px] text-[96px] text-white">PÜSSI</h1>
    <h1 class="font-beardbone xl:text-right text-center select-none xl:text-[300px] text-[96px] text-white xl:pl-[274px]">VESKI</h1>
    <img src="/Wlogo.png" alt="Wlogo" class="select-none xl:w-[600px] w-[130px] xl:h-[600px] h-[130px] absolute xl:top-[160px] top-[200px] xl:left-1/2 xl:-translate-x-1/2 z-[1] opacity-40">
  </div>
</header>
<main>
  <section style="margin-top: 100px; padding-bottom: 100px;">
      <svg  class="absolute md:mt-[70px] mt-[35px] right-0 md:h-[262px] md:w-[254px] h-[117px] w-[117px]">
        <use href="/revolverhalved.svg" fill="#CB2729"  class="md:h-[262px] md:w-[254px] h-[117px] w-[117px]"/>
      </svg>
      <svg  class="md:visible invisible absolute md:mt-[70px] left-0 md:h-[262px] md:w-[254px] h-[117px] w-[117px]">
        <use href="/revolverhalvedflip.svg" fill="#CB2729"  class="md:h-[262px] md:w-[254px] h-[117px] w-[117px]"/>
      </svg>
    <div>
      <div class="pb-[50px] md:flex md:justify-center md:items-center item-start justify-start md:relative md:gap-[6px] md:w-full md:px-[274px] px-[16px]">
        <svg class="md:visible invisible shrink" width="500" height="4">
          <rect width="500" height="4" fill="#CB2729"/>
        </svg>
        <h2 class="font-beardbone text-left md:text-center md:text-[128px] text-[64px] text-primary m-0 shrink">HISTORY</h2>
        <svg class="md:visible invisible shrink" width="500" height="4">
          <rect width="500" height="4" fill="#CB2729"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:gap-[184px] gap-[20px] md:flex lg:px-[274px] px-[16px]">
        <article class="md:w-[328px]">
          <header class="pb-[10px]">
            <h3 class="text-left font-extrabold text-[24px] text-darkness">Creation of Püssi veski</h3>
            <p class="font-light text-[20px] text-golden">1974 - 1986</p>
          </header>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-darkness">
            Püssi Veski was established in 1974 by a group of passionate individuals who shared a vision of creating a unique and welcoming space for the community. The founders, inspired by the rich history of Püssi, aimed to blend tradition with modernity, resulting in a venue that would become a beloved local landmark. <br>
            Over the years, Püssi Veski has evolved, adapting to the changing needs and tastes of its patrons while remaining true to its roots. The dedication to quality and service has made it a staple in the community, attracting visitors from near and far.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="md:w-[328px] md:pt-[150px]">
          <header class="pb-[10px]">
            <h3 class="text-left font-extrabold text-[24px] text-darkness">Creating guns in Püssi</h3>
            <p class="font-light text-[20px] text-golden">1987 - 2001</p>
          </header>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-darkness">
            In the late 1980s, Püssi Veski expanded its offerings to include a unique line of handcrafted firearms. This decision was driven by the growing demand for high-quality, artisanal weapons among collectors and enthusiasts. The guns produced at Püssi Veski quickly gained a reputation for their craftsmanship and attention to detail, attracting buyers from across the region. <br>
            The transition from a traditional venue to a firearms manufacturer marked a significant shift in Püssi Veski's history, showcasing its adaptability and commitment to excellence.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="md:w-[328px]">
          <header class="pb-[10px]">
            <h3 class="text-left font-extrabold text-[24px] text-darkness">New management</h3>
            <p class="font-light text-[20px] text-golden">2002 - Today</p>
          </header>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-darkness">
            In 2002, Püssi Veski underwent a significant management change, bringing in a new team dedicated to revitalizing the brand while preserving its heritage. The new management focused on enhancing the customer experience, introducing innovative products, and expanding the venue's offerings. <br>
            Today, Püssi Veski stands as a testament to its rich history and evolution, continuing to serve the community with pride and excellence. The commitment to quality and tradition remains at the heart of everything they do, ensuring that Püssi Veski will continue to be a cherished part of the local culture for years to come.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="relative">
    <svg class="absolute lg:mt-[35px] mt-[10px] xl:left-[-242px] right-0 z-[-1]" height="304px" width="1530px">
      <use href="/shotgun.svg" fill="#CB2729" height="304px" width="1530px"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="pb-[50px]">
      <h2 class="font-beardbone text-left font-outline-8 lg:px-[274px] px-[16px] lg:text-9xl text-[64px] text-primary m-0 shrink-0">HISTORIC FIGURES</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:px-[274px] pb-[100px] lg:flex gap-[194px] justify-items-center">
      <article class="flex flex-col items-center w-[328px]">
        <header class="md:pb-[10px]">
          <img src="/nedkelly.jpg" alt="Ned Killy" class="sm:w-[328px] w-[160px] sm:h-[328px] h-[160px] rounded-full object-cover md:mb-[20px]">
          <h3 class="text-center font-beardbone md:text-[32px] text-[24px]">Ned Kelly</h3>
        </header>
        <p class="text-center md:text-[16px] text-[14px] text-darkness">
          Ned Kelly was the visionary behind the creation of Püssi Veski, establishing it as a cornerstone of the local community. His leadership and dedication to quality set the standard for generations to come.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="flex flex-col items-center w-[328px] md:pt-0 pt-[20px]">
        <header class="pb-[10px]">
          <img src="/bassreeves.jpg" alt="Bass Pro" class="sm:w-[328px] w-[160px] sm:h-[328px] h-[160px] rounded-full object-cover md:mb-[20px]">
          <h3 class="text-center font-beardbone md:text-[32px] text-[24px]">Bass Reeves</h3>
        </header>
        <p class="text-center md:text-[16px] text-[14px] text-darkness">
          Bass Reeves was a legendary lawman and the first black deputy Estonian Marshal west of the Püssi River. His fearless pursuit of justice and unwavering integrity made him a symbol of courage and resilience in the face of adversity.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="flex flex-col items-center w-[328px] md:pt-0 pt-[20px]">
        <header class="pb-[10px]">
          <img src="/buffalobill.jpg" alt="Buffer my bill" class="sm:w-[328px] w-[160px] sm:h-[328px] h-[160px] rounded-full object-cover md:mb-[20px]">
          <h3 class="text-center font-beardbone md:text-[32px] text-[24px]">"Buffalo" Bill Cody</h3>
        </header>
        <p class="text-center md:text-[16px] text-[14px] text-darkness">
          "Buffalo" Bill Cody was a legendary figure of the Estonian East, known for his Wild West shows that celebrated the frontier spirit. His larger-than-life persona and showmanship captivated audiences, leaving an indelible mark on Estonian culture.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section style="background-color: #CB2729; padding-top: 100px; padding-bottom: 105px; color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div class="relative z-[1] px-[274px] w-fit">
      <h2 class="font-beardbone text-left text-[128px] m-0 shrink-0">Attractions</h2>
      <p class="font-khula text-left text-[16px] pb-[50px] w-[541px]">
      Püssi Veski offers a range of attractions that showcase the rich history and culture of the region. From guided tours of the historic site to interactive exhibits that highlight the craftsmanship behind our artisanal firearms, there is something for everyone to enjoy.
      </p>
      <div>
      <article class="w-[328px] pb-[50px]">
        <header>
        <h3 class="text-left font-extrabold text-[24px]">Tours</h3>
        <p class="font-light text-[20px]">E-R 10:00 - 20:00</p>
        </header>
        <div>
        <p class="text-[16px] pb-[40px]">
          Explore the wonderous landscape of Ida Virumaa and experience the culture of Püssi for yourself in groups of 10.
        </p>
        <button class="outline outline-white outline-2 text-white py-[15px] px-[30px] text-[16px] rounded-[30px]">
          READ MORE
        </button>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="w-[328px]">
        <header>
        <h3 class="text-left font-extrabold text-[24px]">Shooting range</h3>
        <p class="font-light text-[20px]">K-R 15:00 - 20:00</p>
        </header>
        <div>
        <p class="text-[16px] pb-[40px]">
          Try out a wide variety of rifles, revolvers, derringers, and shotguns made right here in Püssi veski.
        </p>
        <button class="outline outline-white outline-2 text-white py-[15px] px-[30px] text-[16px] rounded-[30px]">
          READ MORE
        </button>
        </div>
      </article>
      </div>
    </div>
    <svg style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: -300; width: 200%; z-index: 0;" height="557px" width="1945px">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="landscape-gradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="0">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#CB2729"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#770000"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <use href="/landscape.svg" fill="url(#landscape-gradient)" height="557px" width="1945px"/>
    </svg>
    <div id="auto-scroll-gallery" class="md:absolute relative lg:top-0 lg:right-0 h-full w-[602px] overflow-y-auto flex lg:flex-col gap-0 z-[2] rounded-none p-0 scrollbar-none">
      <img src="/derringer.jpg" alt="Derringer" class="w-full h-[602px] object-cover rounded-none">
      <img src="/winchester.jpg" alt="Winchester" class="w-full h-[602px] object-cover rounded-none">
      <img src="/twinrevolvers.jpg" alt="Twin Revolvers" class="w-full h-[602px] object-cover rounded-none">
      <img src="/derringersg.jpg" alt="Derringer shotgun" class="w-full h-[602px] object-cover rounded-none">
    </div>
    <script>
      (function() {
      const gallery = document.getElementById('auto-scroll-gallery');
      let scrollStep = 1;
      let direction = 1;
      function autoScroll() {
      if (!gallery) return;
      if (direction === 1 && gallery.scrollTop + gallery.clientHeight >= gallery.scrollHeight) {
      direction = -1;
      } else if (direction === -1 && gallery.scrollTop <= 0) {
      direction = 1;
      }
      gallery.scrollTop += scrollStep * direction;
      }
      setInterval(autoScroll, 20);
      })();
    </script>
  </section>
</main>
{% endblock %}